To get a rss url go to https://soundcloud.com and get the url for the podcast
you are interested in and copy the link into https://getrssfeed.com. This will
come up with a link to an rss feed that you can put into the .newsboat/urls
file. Then in news boat go to the rss feed. Find the podcast you want to listen
to and hit *e* to add the podcast to the .newsboat/queue file. Then you can
open podboat to download the file.
